# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# KIMUNTUX BLOCKCHAIN - GIT IGNORE RULES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# CRITICAL: This file prevents sensitive data from being committed to git
#
# ⚠️  WARNING: Committing private keys to git can result in:
#   - Complete loss of funds
#   - Unauthorized contract modifications
#   - Identity theft
#   - Irreversible damage
#
# IF YOU ACCIDENTALLY COMMIT SECRETS:
#   1. Immediately rotate all keys/passwords
#   2. Transfer all funds to new wallets
#   3. Use tools like BFG Repo-Cleaner or git-filter-repo
#   4. Force push cleaned history (breaks all forks)
#   5. Notify team members to re-clone
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SENSITIVE FILES - CRITICAL SECURITY
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Environment variables (NEVER COMMIT THESE!)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.development
.env.test
.env.production

# Private keys and secrets (additional safety)
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
secrets.*
private-keys.*
wallet-*.json
keystore/

# Backup files that might contain secrets
*.backup
*.bak
*.old
*.orig


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# NODE.JS / NPM
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Dependencies
node_modules/
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml
.yarn/*
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/plugins
.pnp.*

# npm debug logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
lerna-debug.log*


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# HARDHAT / ETHEREUM DEVELOPMENT
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Compilation artifacts
cache/
artifacts/
build/
dist/
typechain/
typechain-types/

# Deployment records (contains deployed addresses)
# ⚠️  Keep these if you want to track deployments, ignore if sensitive
deployments/*.json
!deployments/.gitkeep
!deployments/README.md

# Hardhat network files
.openzeppelin/

# Flatten output (may contain full source)
flattened/
*.flattened.sol

# Coverage reports
coverage/
coverage.json
.coverage_artifacts/
.coverage_cache/
.coverage_contracts/

# Gas reports
gas-report.txt
gas-report.json


